vars:pre-request {
  baseUrl: https://api.agent37.com
  proxyDomain: agent37.app
}

docs {
  Collection-level defaults that every request inherits, so the quickstart works
  the moment you open it — the only thing you set yourself is your sk_live_ token.

  - baseUrl     — control plane host. POST/DELETE /v1/instances live here (01, 05).
  - proxyDomain — data plane domain. Each instance answers at
                  https://{instanceId}.agent37.app, so the agent requests (02, 03,
                  04) target https://{{instanceId}}.{{proxyDomain}}/v1/*.

  instanceId and sessionId are not here on purpose: they are filled in at runtime by
  the post-response scripts in 01 and 03 and persisted to your environment.
}
